    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>阿兹特克人</strong>——一支在中美洲大地上持续辉煌了超过三个世纪的文明，曾统治广袤疆域，缔造出在人类历史上独树一帜的社会体系。这个民族远见卓识且充满力量，有丰富的传统、强大的神祇和神圣的仪式。你是 <strong>特拉托阿尼</strong>，一位神圣的阿兹特克人领袖，生来就注定要掌控族人的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409840/extras/433c42613d1ba1b801208b3743e37868.poster.avif?t=1768551804\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409840/extras/433c42613d1ba1b801208b3743e37868.webm?t=1768551804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在特斯科科湖的水面上建造</strong>并<strong>发展壮丽的城邦特诺奇提特兰</strong>。 <strong>夺回宝贵土地</strong>、<strong>养育你的子民</strong>、<strong>建造宏伟建筑</strong>，并维持<strong>连接你的漂浮帝国与墨西哥谷地外部世界的关键贸易路线</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409840/extras/65e7c54515fad0f7ed8509c124f859e5.poster.avif?t=1768551804\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409840/extras/65e7c54515fad0f7ed8509c124f859e5.webm?t=1768551804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但在这些琐碎挣扎之上，一场更<strong>可怕的威胁</strong>正悄然逼近：<strong>月亮女神</strong>已向太阳宣战，向你的追随者降下<strong>可怖的诅咒</strong>。唯有<strong>献祭活人</strong>，奉上鲜血，才能召唤出<strong>守护的神盾</strong>，但其力量转瞬即逝。在黑暗降临前，你的子民还能撑过多少个夜晚？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409840/extras/1239f4edd3431c2a74d244a1f987ba86.avif?t=1768551804\" width=250 height=73 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在特斯科科湖的岛屿上建设并扩展</strong>传奇的城邦<strong>特诺奇提特兰</strong>，利用超过<strong>25种不同类型的建筑</strong>，每种建筑都有各自的升级选项。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在跨越多个章节的史诗剧情任务中，选择将决定命运</strong>，你必须引领子民对抗强大的<strong>超自然敌人</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修建<strong>运河</strong>与<strong>蓄水池</strong>，运用先进的<strong>地形改造系统</strong>，从湖泊中<strong>夺回宝贵的土地</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过<strong>仪式与活人献祭</strong>取悦众神，献上鲜血换取<strong>神圣庇护</strong>，抵御威胁城邦生存的黑暗力量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平衡<strong>经济</strong>、<strong>信仰</strong>与<strong>生存</strong>系统，将难民转化为社会中宝贵的力量。你可以让他们辛勤劳作，或<strong>将其献祭！</strong> 为<strong>俘虏</strong>、<strong>平民</strong>、<strong>贵族</strong>与<strong>祭司</strong>分配各自的职责。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在战略地图上派遣远征队</strong>，深入<strong>墨西哥谷地</strong>各地搜集<strong>资源</strong>、发展<strong>贸易</strong>，确保你的城邦繁荣昌盛。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造<strong>宏伟壮丽的建筑</strong>，如巨大的<strong>神庙</strong>、<strong>学府</strong>与<strong>花园</strong>，展现你文明的辉煌与对神明的虔诚。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409840/extras/7e3f4989af2cc41f998f10aa18f36ed8.poster.avif?t=1768551804\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409840/extras/7e3f4989af2cc41f998f10aa18f36ed8.webm?t=1768551804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
